# The `CaseBlock` Struct Reference

<DoxygenPage pluginConfig={pluginConfig}>

This structure is used to communicate between <a href="/docs/api/classes/llvm/selectiondagbuilder">SelectionDAGBuilder</a> and SDISel for the code generation of additional basic blocks needed by multi-case switch statements. <a href="#details">More...</a>

## Description {#details}
